message.body: Hey britt
Hey darling. How's it going?
Goof. What u up too?
At a graduation party for a little. What about you?
Not much. My friend from out ta town came by earlier but they just left. I wanna do somethin!
Aww well what are you trying to do? Go out to a bar?
Yeah maybe. Hang with some peeps. U up in Lansdale?
Yeah right now I am. I wish you woulda texted me earlier. I woulda headed down that way. Lets do something next Saturday. I'll come down to you. You can
show me the ropes lol. We can go to manayunk or something
I am gonna be at the beach next weekend. What do u think about July 3?
I could do that I think
u think eh??
Yeah I think that might be a good plan
Wait. I lied. I have movie night with the girls at 6:30. Unless I just make it down there kinda late. Up to you
What is late? Like 10?
Umm prob like 10 or 11
Sounds like a late night!
Is that bad?
Nah. Didn't u see my exclamation point? Haha what movie u goin to see?
Hahahah I was hoping you wouldn't be a drag like that lol. And we're going to see the heat, with Sandra bullock and Melissa McCartney
If its not an issue by the way, I may wind up just staying down at your house that night
Yeah that's fine
Ok awesome. Thanks
Yay can't wait for Wednesday now
Awww me too! Reunion!!
